Class DistrictValueMap

    Map<District<?>,OptionalInt>

    public class DistrictValueMap
extends de.larssh.utils.collection.ProxiedMap<District<?>,OptionalInt>
    A map to store numeric values per District. When retrieving data of a higher-level district its value is calculated based on the sum of the values of its children.
